title: (PSX-PSP) Xena: Warrior Princess converted properly (Kingdom-gam
description:
XENA: WARRIOR PRINCESS:

There has been a mishap atop Mount Olympus, and the only person who can resolve it is XENA: Warrior Princess. Kalabrax, a foe whom Xena had previously defeated, has escaped from his prison and is ready to destroy the world for her own benefit. To accomplish this she has captured Gabrielle the Queen of the Amazons and Xena&#039;s friend and plans to sacrifice her. It&#039;s up to you, as Xena, to save your friend and once again take care of Kalabrax. There are 21 different levels of action that will take you all over the mythological world: islands, mountains, and deserts, each with different types of enemies and puzzles. You must use every weapon at your disposal, including your famous Chakram to make your way to Gabrielle. The game also contains magical spells you can use, such as lightning and ice attacks. XENA: Warrior Princess contains all of the energy of the show, though now it all fits into an exciting and compelling interactive experience.
